[SPEAKER_01] ono, Bože, ti ovu kuću,

1333
00:57:22,260 --> 00:57:22,800
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj stan,

1334
00:57:22,800 --> 00:57:24,559
[SPEAKER_01] čini kućom molitve,

1335
00:57:24,559 --> 00:57:26,119
