1346
00:57:44,480 --> 00:57:46,099
[SPEAKER_01] nek dođu pa ćemo moliti zajedno.

1347
00:57:46,099 --> 00:57:48,840
[SPEAKER_01] A oni su čuli da sam se ja okrenuo,

1348
00:57:48,840 --> 00:57:49,519
[SPEAKER_01] obratio,

1349
00:57:49,519 --> 00:57:51,119
[SPEAKER_01] pa su rekli,

1350
00:57:51,119 --> 00:57:51,860
[SPEAKER_01] pa zar i on?

1351
00:57:51,860 --> 00:57:53,340
[SPEAKER_01] Očito je u to vrijeme

1352
00:57:53,340 --> 00:57:55,340
[SPEAKER_01] gospodin radio na mnogima,

1353
00:57:55,340 --> 00:57:57,360
[SPEAKER_01] radio jedan zahvat po Hrvatskoj

1354
00:57:57,360 --> 00:57:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] za mlade,

1355
00:57:58,340 --> 00:57:59,500
[SPEAKER_01] po mladima,

1356
00:57:59,500 --> 00:58:02,599
[SPEAKER_01] vuko ih je nazad u crkvu,

1357
00:58:02,599 --> 00:58:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] tad su naštali Božja pobjeda

1358
00:58:04,340 --> 00:58:05,420
[SPEAKER_01] i mnoge druge zajednice.

1359
00:58:05,420 --> 00:58:07,739
[SPEAKER_01] I tako su, ono,

1360
00:58:07,739 --> 00:58:10,099
[SPEAKER_01] došli su molitelji kod nas doma

1361
