[SPEAKER_01] kroz neko kratko vrijeme

1363
00:58:14,940 --> 00:58:16,340
[SPEAKER_01] kućnu molitvenu grupu

1364
00:58:16,340 --> 00:58:18,239
[SPEAKER_01] koja je rasla sve više i više

1365
00:58:18,239 --> 00:58:20,940
